Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base left Northern Ireland\Nafter repulsing Char's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However, hiding inside the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...was a young woman who had\Nsnuck aboard under Char's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu Ratokie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...wasn't a girl who had become\Na spy by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that, Ms. Sayla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna stall!\NPlease hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Docking completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. That's just 15 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just as Amuro had pointed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Gundam docked to become G-Bull,\Nthe left side was totally unprotected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding a solution to cover\Nthis weakness in the armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...would be a top priority for improving\Nthe Gundam's modular system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base crew are presently\Nabove the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Their destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the Atlantic Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The whale from the Federation Forces\Nwas a lot larger than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! We've received a message\Nfrom Captain Boone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From Boone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That Boone. He sent a spy\Nto infiltrate the Trojan Horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But how does he plan to retrieve the intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sneak Into an officer's room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, find out their Intended destination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Second, collect any data on the.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have that information ready for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to head up to the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Guess he's already gone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what tore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\ND-Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's you, Miharu!\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Where'd you get that uniform...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your little sister and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true that you came here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie!\NIt's... it's partly true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh... You'd better come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such tactless questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop her off in South America.\NSo keep it a secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I didn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it... See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The key code for the door is 3986.\NStay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in South America are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed for a spaceship dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's about all the information\Nyou're gonna get out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If the White Base blew up before reaching\NSouth America, neither of us would survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll contact you on your wrist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much time.\NWhat's he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilian aircraft approaching\Nat 4 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sending out a distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A distress signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's a civilian aircraft?\NCan you confirm that, Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I'm confirming it right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,According to its registration number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...it belongs to a fishery union\Nin the Verde Islands, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Instruct them to enter from the rear deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Open Deck 4!\NPrepare to dock civilian plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet we're the first Zeons\Nto infiltrate the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't say a word.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your Zeon accent is too strong.\N- Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry with that!\NIt'll catch fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were out checking for schools of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A Zeon fighter plane\Nstarted shooting at us for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- When?\N- About 20 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been shot with unexploded\N20mm shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do makeshift repairs and provide you\Nwith enough fuel to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Appreciate it.\N- However, you'll be restricted to that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, that's fine with me...\NHey! Carioca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll send a repair invoice to the union.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't charge too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. You think anyone at the union\Nwill accept the invoice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's the toilet?\N- Oh. Go straight, then turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right, there!\NDon't go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose this is all new to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. 107. If you can speak aloud, answer me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's the Trojan Horse heading?\N- A spaceship dock in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good. What else?\N- Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.\NKeep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you contact them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you reach them from this distance?\NIt doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how my family and I\Nhave been able to feed ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm getting you in trouble.\NMe being a spy and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They said a civilian aircraft came on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way they\Ncould reach you by radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Whatever happens after this\Nhas got nothing to do with you. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My sixth sense told me there's something\Nsuspicious about that civilian aircraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Someone make that aircraft stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're spies!\NShoot 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mr. Kai?\NThey're just fishermen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange they approached\Nthe White Base at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright! You sure those guys weren't spies?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we checked it all out.\NWe frisked the pilots as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We even confirmed that the airplane\Ngenuinely belongs to a fishery union.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y- Yeah, but still...It's possible that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai. Do you happen to have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, no. It's just strangeour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not the African front?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're definitely headed for a\Nspaceship dock in South America, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they're not coming this way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Angler has to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to observe\Nthe situation on the African front.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a pilot in my younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,May I borrow the mobile armor, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grabro...? It's certainly ready, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to call it "revenge", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So far they've managed to sink\Nfour of my mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me attack them.\NIf I use that mobile armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...even from this distance,\Nit'll catch up to the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven't gone.\NThey've appeared at 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a submarine could\Ncatch up to us. Just watch for missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming! Missiles detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire rear missiles!\N7 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A second and third wave of missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Fourth and fifth wave\Napproaching from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack the submarine!\NAll units standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's hard to decide what to deploy\Nwhen we barely know about our opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're over the ocean, so the Guncannon\Nand Guntank are at a disadvantage. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai says mobile suits are heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too. In that case, let's use\Nthe Gundam and G-Fighter separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Objects approaching at 10 o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All hands, prepare for battle!\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Portside! Put up a barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's lift, all together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are children on this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take off in G-Armor mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- We can bolt out in mid-air.\N- Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll avenge all of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. Is the White Base badly damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. It looks like they\Nonly got part of the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What part of the ship was just hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Deck 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Deck 2, give me a damage report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wear this life jacket!\NIt's all for nothing if you don't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you?\N- I'm in the middle of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are in danger, Mr. Kai,\Nall because I gave them information...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The little information you gave them\Nwouldn't result in an attack like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Kai! I'm the one who...!\NThis is all my fault, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hey! Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro. Here we go. Gundam, bolt out!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,4, 3, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?!\NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally showed up, Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Confident in your underwater combat skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you underestimating ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Fighter power at 90, 95...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,100! 120! Launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All blocks, give me a damage report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we send out Kai's Core Fighter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The catapult's damaged.hters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the Gunperry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's equipped with anti-submarine missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh. You're right, sir.t away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! Get them to open Deck 3!\NWe'll be sending out the Gunperry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!\NDeck 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the Gunperry for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai, where are you?\NPlease proceed to Deck 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai to Deck 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu, hide someplace\Nwhere you can easily escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone's fighting!\NLet me help! Please! I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...! You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They've sunk Godard's Z'Gok!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the White Base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thruster output, decreased by 40 percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know! Tell the crew to aim well\Nbefore firing the anti-submarine missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! How's the Gundam doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no response yet.\NI think he's struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the Gundam isn't equipped\Nwith any weapons for underwater use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't say that!\N- Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of weapons does this guy have\Nfor underwater combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. If I don't lure him to the surface,\Nthe Gundam doesn't have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You foolishly came underwater\Nto fight against my Grabro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I feared, the beam rifle's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...is halved when fired underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that!\NI've got you now, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, we're fine.\NThis is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! You kids are brave and strong!\NKeep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Please give me the chance to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let these kids die\Nwhen my sister and brother are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikka! Come on!\NThere're still some fires to put out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go back, I'll just continue\Nbeing used by Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I can't bear to just stand here,\Nwatching from the sidelines!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai! Please take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Where is Job right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's busy firing the machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!\NI need a bombardier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can launch missiles, can't you?!\N- Just tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for this mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as helpless as a baby\Nbefore the power of my Grabro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the enemy blip\Nin the scope's cross-hairs, fire the missile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of bullets and missiles!\NMr. Kai, please take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You press one lever at a time!\NJust stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That one missed!\NNext one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! I pressed the lever but it won't fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Not now, at a time like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...\NThat attack damaged the electrical circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we defeat the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could move the lever\Non the side of the catapult...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! You said there's a lever\Non the side of the catapult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Listen, you gotta do it properly!\NYou know how to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Steer the plane toward the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! The enemy's coming straight at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Miharu! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The other Z'Gok was destroyed as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mistake was tearing off\Nthe Gundam's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's allowed me to move more easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miharu! What's keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back up here, Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Kai! Watch out!e ship now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And this Miharu disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Apparently, she and Kai launched\Ntogether on the Gunperry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is she?\NDo you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir. Nobody knows her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a stowaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A stowaway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a young lady go into Mr. Kai's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the enemy showed up, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu... She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gil and Milly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll live a much better life than we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the world won't be this awful\Nforever, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Federation Forces Headquarters at Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Char commands an assault on the base...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...while Amuro runs into Matilda's fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,War mercilessly destroys a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...as well as anger, and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam.\NTragedy in Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragedy in Jaburo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:24:00.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:10.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:15.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.81,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:25.19,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:29.78,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:40.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:24:00.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:10.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:15.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:25.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:29.78,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:40.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
